description:
On today’s show, we’re on the Sex with Emily hotline, taking your calls and answering your sex questions live!

Want to step up your squirting game? Curious about exploring the swinger lifestyle? Wondering if it’s time to end a lackluster marriage? Maybe you’re just dying to know what Anderson’s favorite part of his newfound fatherhood is! Find the answers to these questions and more on today’s live call-in show. So listen close, you won’t want to miss a beat.

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
